author: Ava
title: US approves 'final' military aid package to Ukraine | DW News
text:
Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy on Thursday thanked "Joe Biden, Congress, and the American people" for the latest $250 million (roughly €225 million) military aid package announced late on Wednesday. The tranche of aid is the last for the year, and as the White House appeals to Congress to approve more funds urgently, warning that failure to do so will lead to available resources running out by the end of the year.
